                      <p>&nbsp;</p>
                      <p>FINANCE CHARGE AND PAYMENTS. We will compute your Finance Charge on a daily basis at the Annual Percentage Rate on the unpaid part of the Amount Financed. We based the Finance Charge, Total of Payments and the Total Sale Price shown in this contract on the assumption that you will make each payment in the amount due and on the date due. These amounts will be more if you pay late and less if you pay early. These changes may take the form of a larger or smaller last payment or, if we choose, additional payments of the same amount as your scheduled payments with a smaller final payment. We will notify you about these changes before your final scheduled payment is due. </p>
                    </td>
                    <td width="51%" align="left" valign="top">
